Mojolicious-Plugin-UrlToken version 0.0.1

This module provides a helper generate_url_token that creates a unique token for use in email validation

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

Mojolicious
Data::UUID
MIME::Base64::URLSafe


